    <title>Install Tomcat on Mac OS</title>
    <link href="https://tarik.io/en/tools/tomcat/2017/06/18/install-tomcat-on-mac-os/"/>
    <id>https://tarik.io/en/tools/tomcat/2017/06/18/install-tomcat-on-mac-os/</id>
    <published>2017-06-18T11:18:32.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-06-18T11:33:30.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Recently, embedded Tomcat in spring-boot caused problems with a dependency. Migrating to standalone Tomcat solved it luckily.</p>
<p>Installing Tomcat on Mac OS is very simple if you have <code>brew</code> installed:<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">brew install tomcat</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>You can run Tomcat with following command after the installation (you may need to replace directory <em>8.5.15</em> with your own installed version):<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">/usr/<span class="built_in">local</span>/Cellar/tomcat/8.5.15/bin/catalina run</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>You should be able to see default tomcat page now:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://localhost:8080/" target="_blank" rel="external">http://localhost:8080/</a></li>
</ul>
<p>Deploying your application is also very simple. Copying the <em>.war</em> file to <em>webapps</em> folder will trigger the deployment.<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">cp app.war /usr/<span class="built_in">local</span>/Cellar/tomcat/8.5.15/libexec/webapps/</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>References:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://maltronic.io/2016/01/14/easily-install-apache-tomcat-on-mac-os-x-10-11-el-capitan-with-homebrew/" target="_blank" rel="external">https://maltronic.io/2016/01/14/easily-install-apache-tomcat-on-mac-os-x-10-11-el-capitan-with-homebrew/</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.baeldung.com/tomcat-deploy-war#Copying" target="_blank" rel="external">http://www.baeldung.com/tomcat-deploy-war#Copying</a></li>
</ul>
]]></content>
    
